{"type": "article", "id": 3513, "title": "KOMONO 2014秋冬配饰系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-13T08:06:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232928R9DshuKHxMLYNEFT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自比利时的腕表品牌 KOMONO 虽然短短创立仅 5年，但凭借其精细的手工几亿与高质量，已经收获了不少忠实买家。日前，KOMONO 推出了 2014 秋冬配件系列「The Places In Between」，寓意没有起点，没有终点，始终在路上的旅行的意义。这一系列结合了复古与未来两种不同的元素，包括数款样式不一的眼镜与腕表，不管是金属网表带的 Winston Royale 腕表，橡胶框架的 Dreyfuss 太阳眼镜还是经典轮廓的 Clement 眼镜，都可以作为一款特别的圣诞礼物送给自己。定价44.95－89.95 欧元不等，<a href=\"http://shop.komono.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232925duH9a1jntCYN4KM7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232926rt2L0Xf6YgdMRUoP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232926HsQSzyhfaILvVedg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232927ZrRhx0Vjt7pFbDAo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052329271Mv4zfewlJQjnETg.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}